pload: The system will maintain the original folder structure upon upload. -- 1 of 4 -- ‚Ä¢ Background Uploading: Uploads will continue in the background, allowing the user to continue working within the application. ‚Ä¢ Import from Cloud Storage: Direct integration with services like Google Drive, Dropbox, and OneDrive for seamless mass import of files and folders. AI-Powered Organization ‚Ä¢ Natural Language Commands: Users can interact with the AI to manage their documents using simple, conversational language. For example, a user could say, "Hey Koda, file this invoice in the 'Business Expenses 2025' folder. " ‚Ä¢ Automated Sorting and Tagging: The AI will automatically analyze the content of new documents and suggest relevant folders and tags based on the user's existing organizational structure and past behavior. ‚Ä¢ Smart Folder Creation: The AI can create new folders and organizational structures based on the user's needs. For example, a user could ask, "Hey Koda, create a new project folder for the 'Q4 Marketing Campaign'. " ‚Ä¢ Duplicate Detection: The AI will identify and flag duplicate documents to help users maintain a clean and organized document library. Search and Retrieval ‚Ä¢ Advanced Search & Filtering: Users can find files by name, type, tag, and content. The search functionality will be fast and accurate, even with a large number of documents. ‚Ä¢ Cross-Document Referencing: The AI can search and synthesize information across all documents in the user's system to provide comprehensive answers to complex questions. Document Lifecycle ‚Ä¢ Trash & Restore: Deleted documents can be easily restored within a specified timeframe, preventing accidental data loss. ‚Ä¢ Version History: The system will keep a history of document versions, allowing users to view and restore previous versions of their files. 4. Smart Reminders & Notifications Smart Reminders ‚Ä¢ AI-Powered Date Extraction: The AI will automatically scan documents for important dates, such as